18 June 2020 V4-1-11-R315
        - Updated for EPICS R3.15
        - Removed get_value() from RSETs, since this record support function doesn't exist
          any more in EPICS R3.15
        - calls to dbGetLinkValue() changed to dbGetLink() 
          because dbGetLinkValue() no longer exists -- it was never supposed to be called directly
          anyway, but via the dbGetLink() macro.
        - dbGetLink() is now a function instead of a macro, so 
          #include <dbLink.h> had to be added to all xxxRecord.c files
        - Cleanup of unused variables in several modules
